OL,3,CSevern Trent given power to fill
OL,4,Creservoirs with river water as drought
OL,5,Cpersists
OL,7,FThe Environment Agency has given
OL,8,FSevern Trent permission to use river
OL,9,Fwater to refill reservoirs in the East
OL,10,FMidlands as drought continues to hit
OL,11,Fthe region.
OL,13,FThe authority has approved a drought
OL,14,Fpermit application to Severn Trent,
OL,15,Fgiving them permission to secure water
OL,16,Ffrom River Derwent at Ambergate to
OL,17,Ffill Carsington and Ogston reservoirs
OL,18,Fin Derbyshire.
