OL,3,CSevern Trent given power to fill
OL,4,Creservoirs with river water as drought
OL,5,Cpersists
OL,7,FThe drought permit will allow Severn
OL,8,FTrent to take action to conserve the
OL,9,Fpublic water supply - with drought
OL,10,Fconditions expected to persist into
OL,11,Fnext year.
OL,13,FThe Environment Agency's announcement
OL,14,Ffollows England's driest start to the
OL,15,Fyear since 1976, leaving many rivers
OL,16,Facross the Midlands at extremely low
OL,17,Flevels.
