OL,3,CSevern Trent given power to fill
OL,4,Creservoirs with river water as drought
OL,5,Cpersists
OL,7,FThe drought permit changes abstraction
OL,8,Flicence conditions state when and how
OL,9,Fmuch water can be taken from the River
OL,10,FDerwent.
OL,12,FSevern Trent can implement this permit
OL,13,Fif rainfall in the Midlands continues
OL,14,Fto fall below average.
OL,16,FHowever, Severn Trent Water will have
OL,17,Fto inform the Environment Agency
OL,18,Fbefore using the drought permit.
