OL,5,Cpersists
OL,7,FThey will also have to carry out
OL,8,Fmonitoring and mitigation to assess
OL,9,Fand manage potential environmental
OL,10,Fimpacts.
OL,12,FBryan Hemmings, East Midlands Drought
OL,13,FManager at the Environment Agency,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We only issue a drought permit
OL,15,Fif there are clear plans in place to
OL,16,Fmitigate any impact on the environment
OL,17,F` along with strong evidence from the
OL,18,Fwater company of their ongoing
OL,19,Fcommitment to reduce leaks, improve
OL,20,Fwater efficiency and conserve water.
