OL,3,CSevern Trent given power to fill
OL,4,Creservoirs with river water as drought
OL,5,Cpersists
OL,7,F"We'll continue to work closely with
OL,8,FSevern Trent Water as it develops long-
OL,9,Fterm solutions to protect water
OL,10,Fresources while drought conditions
OL,11,Fcontinue across East Midlands."
OL,13,FThis comes as part of extra measures
OL,14,Fto conserve water supplies in the East
OL,15,Fand West Midlands which have
OL,16,Fofficially moved into drought - with
OL,17,Fsome river flows at their lowest in
OL,18,Falmost 50 years.
