OL,3,CSevern Trent given power to fill
OL,4,Creservoirs with river water as drought
OL,5,Cpersists
OL,7,FWater levels in reservoirs across East
OL,8,FMidlands are half what they normally
OL,9,Fare this time of the year, according
OL,10,Fto statistics from the Environment
OL,11,FAgency.
OL,13,FAt the end of October, total they were
OL,14,F48% full, compared with 88% at the
OL,15,Fsame time last year, figures show.
OL,17,FThe decision to declare a drought is
OL,18,Fbased on reservoir levels, river
OL,19,Fflows, how dry soils are and long-term
OL,20,Fweather forecasts.
