OL,3,CSevern Trent given power to fill
OL,4,Creservoirs with river water as drought
OL,5,Cpersists
OL,7,FA Severn Trent spokesperson said: "The
OL,8,FMidlands was declared as being in
OL,9,Fdrought following a record-breaking
OL,10,Fdry spring and summer, the driest and
OL,11,Fwarmest on record, which has resulted
OL,12,Fin less water in rivers and reservoirs.
OL,14,F"This drought permit will support the
OL,15,Frefill of Carsington and Ogston
OL,16,FReservoirs which supply customers in
OL,17,Fthe Derbyshire and Leicestershire
OL,18,Fareas, and helps us plan and prepare
OL,19,Ffor summer 2026.
