OL,7,F"We're continuing our efforts to drive
OL,8,Fdown leakage and we always ask
OL,9,Fcustomers to be mindful about their
OL,10,Fwater usage.
OL,12,F"There are over 2 million people
OL,13,Fliving across both regions, so even
OL,14,Fjust saving a litre a day each would
OL,15,Fmake a big difference."
